snippet.title: China: The Forbidden City - Game Trailer (FR, 1998)
snippet.description:
China: The Forbidden City - game trailer (french)

Developed  by Cryo Interactive Entertainment, , Canal+ Multimedia, Réunion des Musées Nationaux
Published by Cryo  in late 1998 for PC (Windows) and Macintosh, then in 1999 for Playstation.

Year :  1998
Platform :  PC (windows)
Trailer found on  the coverdisc of the french magazine PC Team (issue 38, September 1998)

Game Title :
Chine: Intrigue dans la cité interdite (France)
China: The Forbidden City (US/UK)
Kina: Mysteriet I Den Förbjudna Staden (Sweden)
China: Verrat in der verbotenen Stadt (Germany)
China: Intriges in de verboden stad (Nederlands)
China: Crimen en la Ciudad Prohibida (Spain)
